opengl module for Qore
version 0.0.1 by David Nichols

Requires qore 0.7.0 and opengl headers and libraries to build.

Documentation in docs/opengl-module-doc.html (using TiddlyWiki)

test/example script directory: test/

BUILD AND INSTALL
-----------------

configure
make
sudo make install

The configure script will find out where your qore module directory is found and set this for the install directory.

BUILD FROM SVN
--------------

reconf.sh
configure
make
sudo make install
